main event: An observer reported seeing a bright white object with colored lights in Delmar, New York in October 1968.
interesting points: The sighting lasted over an hour,The object was described as having several colored lights including red, green, yellow, and bright white,The observer did not return the required SIGHTING DATA and SUPPLEMENTAL DATA forms,The report concluded there was insufficient data for evaluation, The object remained stationary during the observation period.
sighted object: bright white object with colored lights
witness description: The observer is described as a reputable citizen who expressed concern over the strange movements of the object.
